{"tid":1893680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"煌府：新港中心店2月8日已暫停開放　衛生署資料不準確","createTime":"2020-02-23T12:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T12:12:11.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c77fe2642bb4d3a4e952ca71278b0c6bf19ecf2","tid":1893680,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200223/s00010/72534772bc254e36a0abbdae6d67bd91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200223%2Fs00010%2F72534772bc254e36a0abbdae6d67bd91.jpg&h=062a593e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衛生署衛生防護中心今日公布，一名任職保安的新型冠狀病毒確診者曾在2月10日，在新港中心煌府分店出席公司飯局。煌府母企首灃控股（1703）發言人表示，該分店自2月8日起已暫停開放，2月10日並無招待任何客人。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，集團翻查記錄，只在1月10日曾有物業保安公司舉行宴會。煌府負責人已致電衛生署，通知其所述確診者2月10日在煌府用膳資料不準確。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1582457783870&amp;issue=20200223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1582457783870%26issue%3D20200223&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAygy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=74943072\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1582457783870&amp;issue=20200223</a>"},{"pid":"3818f38bfe74eb84b5241c83426049c96633d96f","tid":1893680,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}